[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 8413,
        "end_time": 11747,
        "text": "We read fiction for many reasons."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11747,
        "end_time": 12747,
        "text": "To be entertained,"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12747,
        "end_time": 15000,
        "text": "to find out who done it,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 15000,
        "end_time": 18049,
        "text": "to travel to strange, new planets,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 18049,
        "end_time": 19169,
        "text": "to be scared,"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 19169,
        "end_time": 19911,
        "text": "to laugh,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 19911,
        "end_time": 21290,
        "text": "to cry,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 21290,
        "end_time": 22028,
        "text": "to think,"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 22028,
        "end_time": 23153,
        "text": "to feel,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 23153,
        "end_time": 28294,
        "text": "to be so absorbed that for a while\nwe forget where we are."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 28294,
        "end_time": 30954,
        "text": "So, how about writing fiction?"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 30954,
        "end_time": 33559,
        "text": "How do you suck your readers\ninto your stories?"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 33559,
        "end_time": 35983,
        "text": "With an exciting plot? Maybe."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 35983,
        "end_time": 38715,
        "text": "Fascinating characters? Probably."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 38715,
        "end_time": 43401,
        "text": "Beautiful language? Perhaps."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 43401,
        "end_time": 48344,
        "text": "&quot;Billie&#39;s legs are noodles. The ends of\nher hair are poison needles."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 48344,
        "end_time": 53414,
        "text": "Her tongue is a bristly sponge,\nand her eyes are bags of bleach.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 53414,
        "end_time": 57590,
        "text": "Did that description almost make you feel\nas queasy as Billie?"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 57590,
        "end_time": 60803,
        "text": "We grasp that Billie&#39;s legs \naren&#39;t actually noodles."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 60803,
        "end_time": 64268,
        "text": "To Billie, they feel \nas limp as cooked noodles."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 64268,
        "end_time": 67223,
        "text": "It&#39;s an implied comparison, a metaphor."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 67223,
        "end_time": 70239,
        "text": "So, why not simply write it like this?"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 70239,
        "end_time": 72961,
        "text": "&quot;Billie feels nauseated and weak.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 72961,
        "end_time": 78000,
        "text": "Chances are the second description\nwasn&#39;t as vivid to you as the first."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 78000,
        "end_time": 81118,
        "text": "The point of fiction is to cast a spell,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 81118,
        "end_time": 85769,
        "text": "a momentary illusion that you are living\nin the world of the story."
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 85769,
        "end_time": 88077,
        "text": "Fiction engages the senses,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 88077,
        "end_time": 90723,
        "text": "helps us create vivid mental simulacra"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 90723,
        "end_time": 93571,
        "text": "of the experiences \nthe characters are having."
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 93571,
        "end_time": 97329,
        "text": "Stage and screen engage \nsome of our senses directly."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 97329,
        "end_time": 101727,
        "text": "We see and hear the interactions\nof the characters and the setting."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 101727,
        "end_time": 103297,
        "text": "But with prose fiction,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 103297,
        "end_time": 107531,
        "text": "all you have is static symbols\non a contrasting background."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 107531,
        "end_time": 111803,
        "text": "If you describe the story\nin matter of fact, non-tactile language,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 111803,
        "end_time": 114211,
        "text": "the spell risks being a weak one."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 114211,
        "end_time": 117959,
        "text": "Your reader may not get much beyond\ninterpreting the squiggles."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 117959,
        "end_time": 120171,
        "text": "She will understand \nwhat Billie feels like,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 120171,
        "end_time": 123762,
        "text": "but she won&#39;t feel what Billie feels."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 123762,
        "end_time": 127454,
        "text": "She&#39;ll be reading, not immersed\nin the world of the story,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 127454,
        "end_time": 132753,
        "text": "discovering the truths of Billie&#39;s life\nat the same time that Billie herself does."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 132753,
        "end_time": 135667,
        "text": "Fiction plays with our senses:"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 135667,
        "end_time": 136528,
        "text": "taste,"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 136528,
        "end_time": 137658,
        "text": "smell,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 137658,
        "end_time": 138709,
        "text": "touch,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 138709,
        "end_time": 139900,
        "text": "hearing,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 139900,
        "end_time": 141240,
        "text": "sight,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 141240,
        "end_time": 143135,
        "text": "and the sense of motion."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 143135,
        "end_time": 148786,
        "text": "It also plays with our ability to abstract\nand make complex associations."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 148786,
        "end_time": 150816,
        "text": "Look at the following sentence."
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 150816,
        "end_time": 152965,
        "text": "&quot;The world was ghost-quiet,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 152965,
        "end_time": 158106,
        "text": "except for the crack of sails\nand the burbling of water against hull.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 158106,
        "end_time": 160769,
        "text": "The words, &quot;quiet,&quot; &quot;crack,&quot; \nand &quot;burbling,&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 160769,
        "end_time": 163465,
        "text": "engage the sense of hearing."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 163465,
        "end_time": 167288,
        "text": "Notice that Buckell doesn&#39;t use\nthe generic word sound."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 167288,
        "end_time": 172752,
        "text": "Each word he chooses evokes \na particular quality of sound."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 172752,
        "end_time": 176280,
        "text": "Then, like an artist laying \non washes of color"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 176280,
        "end_time": 179142,
        "text": "to give the sense \nof texture to a painting,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 179142,
        "end_time": 183723,
        "text": "he adds anoter layer, motion,\n&quot;the crack of sails,&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 183723,
        "end_time": 188186,
        "text": "and touch, \n&quot;the burbling of water against hull.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 188186,
        "end_time": 191174,
        "text": "Finally, he gives us \nan abstract connection"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 191174,
        "end_time": 194574,
        "text": "by linking the word quiet\nwith the word ghost."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 194574,
        "end_time": 196843,
        "text": "Not &quot;quiet as a ghost,&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 196843,
        "end_time": 198944,
        "text": "which would put \na distancing layer of simile"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 198944,
        "end_time": 201324,
        "text": "between the reader and the experience."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 201324,
        "end_time": 205626,
        "text": "Instead, Buckell creates \nthe metaphor &quot;ghost-quiet&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 205626,
        "end_time": 209132,
        "text": "for an implied, \nrather than overt, comparison."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 209132,
        "end_time": 211790,
        "text": "Writers are always told to avoid cliches"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 211790,
        "end_time": 216232,
        "text": "because there&#39;s very little engagement\nfor the reader in an overused image,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 216232,
        "end_time": 218482,
        "text": "such as &quot;red as a rose.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 218482,
        "end_time": 219251,
        "text": "But give them,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 219251,
        "end_time": 222083,
        "text": "&quot;Love...began on a beach."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 222083,
        "end_time": 227083,
        "text": "It began that day when Jacob saw Anette\nin her stewed-cherry dress,&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 227083,
        "end_time": 229783,
        "text": "and their brains engage \nin the absorbing task"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 229783,
        "end_time": 233186,
        "text": "of figuring out what \na stewed-cherry dress is like."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 233186,
        "end_time": 236809,
        "text": "Suddenly, they&#39;re on a beach\nabout to fall in love."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 236809,
        "end_time": 241498,
        "text": "They&#39;re experiencing the story\nat both a visceral and a conceptual level,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 241498,
        "end_time": 244188,
        "text": "meeting the writer halfway\nin the imaginative play"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 244188,
        "end_time": 247986,
        "text": "of creating a dynamic world\nof the senses."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 247986,
        "end_time": 251135,
        "text": "So when you write, \nuse well-chosen words"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 251135,
        "end_time": 256341,
        "text": "to engage sound, sight, taste,\ntouch, smell, and movement."
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 256341,
        "end_time": 260758,
        "text": "Then create unexpected connotations\namong your story elements,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 260758,
        "end_time": 264666,
        "text": "and set your readers&#39; brushfire \nimaginations alight."
    }
]